title: VA-Dance W Lance v3 D11-Bananazz-08-HQMP3-DJKonabuzz
description:
DJ KonaBuzz (c) presents:
Dance With Lance (C) Version 3.0 Disk 11 Bananazz
High Quality MP3 files from beatmixed DJ set
CD Quality WAV versions at http://djkonabuzz.blogspot.com
Mostly Pop/Dance Vibe tho some trax have a hip hop, electro, alternative, or world music feeling.  Most tracks are 

favorites of mine or my partners that we have been trying to figure out how to work into some mix, so instead of 

continuing to put it off, I took most of the bunch and threw them into the blender.  Oh, there is also a track I 

remixed because every time the original version came on the radio (about once an hour) my whole household was 

rolling their eyes.  Seems a certain badd puppy needed neutering to change the tune... unfortunately, we used 

helium for anesthesia he he ;-)

Many mashups/remixes. Hope you enjoy these.  Thank Gwen Stefani and Bananarama for the disk title, though some of 

the other trax are also kinda goofy.

Note:  I am changing the location of CD quality .WAV files to my blog in order to save some disk space and 

bandwidth on this end.  WAV files are now posted for direct (not torrent) download at 
 <a href="
http://djkonabuzz.blogspot.com" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://djkonabuzz.blogspot.com</a>
